Rating: 3
Good concept but not exceptional flavor. A little bit too much herbs. Next time I would go for a more traditional lobster roll flavor, mostly just lobster and mayo. Also, I think the quantity of stuffing wasn't sufficient for the amount of bread. I used potato rolls which were smaller than small dinner rolls, I cut a notch of bread out of these to put the filling into, but even then, there was barely more than a tablespoon of lobster mix. I would double the recipe next time for the same 24 rolls.

